<!DOCTYPE html>

<html lang="en">

<head>

```
<meta charset="UTF-8">

<meta
    name="viewport"
    content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">

<title>
    CampusConnect
</title>

<link
    href="https://cdnjs.cloudflare.com/ajax/libs/font-awesome/6.5.2/css/all.min.css"
    rel="stylesheet">

<link
    href="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap@5.3.3/dist/css/bootstrap.min.css"
    rel="stylesheet">

<style>

    body{
    background:
    linear-gradient(
        135deg,
        #e0f2fe 0%,
        #dbeafe 25%,
        #f5f3ff 50%,
        #ecfeff 75%,
        #ffffff 100%
    );

    background-attachment: fixed;
    min-height:100vh;
}

    .navbar{
    background:rgba(15,23,42,0.85);
    backdrop-filter:blur(20px);
    box-shadow:
    0 8px 32px rgba(0,0,0,0.15);
    }

    .navbar-brand{
        font-weight:bold;
        font-size:1.4rem;
    }

    .main-container{
        min-height:90vh;
    }

    .card{
        border:none;
        border-radius:15px;
    }

    .btn{
        border-radius:10px;
    }

</style>
```

</head>

<body>

<nav class="navbar navbar-expand-lg sticky-top"></nav>
<div class="container">

<a class="navbar-brand d-flex align-items-center" href="/posts">
    <img src="/images/clogo.png"
         alt="CampusConnect"
         width="50"
         height="50"
         class="me-2">
    <span>CampusConnect</span>
</a>

<button
class="navbar-toggler"
type="button"
data-bs-toggle="collapse"
data-bs-target="#navbarNav">

<span class="navbar-toggler-icon"></span>

</button>

<div
class="collapse navbar-collapse"
id="navbarNav">

<div class="navbar-nav ms-auto gap-2">

<a href="/posts" class="btn btn-light">
Posts
</a>

<a href="/posts/new" class="btn btn-success">
New Post
</a>

<a href="/profile" class="btn btn-primary">
Profile
</a>

<a href="/my-posts" class="btn btn-outline-light">
My Posts
</a>

<a href="/notifications" class="btn btn-warning">
🔔
</a>

<a href="/logout" class="btn btn-danger">
Logout
</a>

</div>

</div>

</div>

</nav>

<div class="container mt-4 main-container">

<%- body %>

</div>

<footer
class="bg-dark text-white text-center p-3 mt-5">

CampusConnect © 2026

</footer>

<script
src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap@5.3.3/dist/js/bootstrap.bundle.min.js">
</script>

</body>

</html>